Interface SubPolicyAssertionMarshaller

All Superinterfaces:
AssertionMarshaller
public interface SubPolicyAssertionMarshaller
extends AssertionMarshaller

This is a special type of AssertionMarshaller that requires a instance of PolicyMarshaller to be used to marshall the nested Assertion into sub Policy elements.
